@notice Mint a Guardian NFT for a user
@dev Each address can only have one Guardian
@param path The Guardian specialization path to choose

@notice Mint a Guardian NFT with initial retirement credit
@param user User to mint for
@param initialRetirement Initial retirement amount to credit
@param path The Guardian specialization path

@notice Record a carbon retirement for a user
@param user User who retired carbon
@param amount Amount retired (in wei)

@notice Set authorized updater (e.g., CarbonCreditToken contract)
@param updater Address to authorize
@param authorized Whether to authorize

@notice Get the fee discount for a user in basis points
@param user User address
@return discount Discount in basis points (e.g., 200 = 2%)

@notice Get the fee reduction for a user in basis points
@param user User address
@return reduction Fee reduction in basis points (e.g., 8000 = 80%)

@notice Get the unlock fee for a token
@param tokenId Guardian token ID
@return fee Unlock fee in wei

@notice Check if a Guardian is transferable
@param tokenId Guardian token ID
@return Whether the Guardian is transferable

@notice Get the Guardian path for a user
@param user User address
@return path The Guardian's path

@notice Get Guardian metadata
@param tokenId Guardian token ID
@return guardian Guardian struct

@notice Get tier thresholds
@param tier Tier to check
@return threshold Carbon retirement threshold (in wei)

@notice Calculate progress to next tier
@param user User address
@return currentTier Current tier
@return nextTier Next tier (same as current if Legendary)
@return progress Progress percentage (0-100)
@return amountToNext Amount needed for next tier
